{"tid":36931,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"無人成日喺街度唱粗口歌","createTime":"2016-12-13T04:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T05:51:22.000Z","uid":60128,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78df7ab76e6c979b1b6825f21106fe36a187f152","tid":36931,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"我出街時，好多時候會不其然唱粗口歌。<br />\n記得有一次，以為周圍無人，放聲高歌仲跳埋開心舞，唱：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;12隻恐龍去叫雞，屌到你老母扑扑趣趣。<br />\n22個龜頭快快樂樂，i fuck u on my way。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但當我忘我地高聲放歌仲用埋震音唱到屌你老母時，後面突然有人高速行過，仲用怪異眼神回望我。<br />\n那一刻，我用了0.237秒諗如何是好，最後唯有對住我左邊無人的空氣講：<br />\n&quot;都叫你唔好上我身架啦，比人見到幾唔好意思。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n然後用癡線佬的眼視對佢笑一笑，嚇到那人走都走唔切。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2412f9b6569d86bdd9a177c1f580c0c9ed7a53","tid":36931,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:52:51.000Z","msg":"打錯題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人成日喺街度唱粗口歌"},{"pid":"6d45533ed728fcee8e246ecd9103559e81d0a611","tid":36931,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:52:51.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"27c3792b98f666dc7bc47079c1e85d8e2919f2bd","tid":36931,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">情憑誰來定錯對</span></span>"},{"pid":"f19c1c36dec501587211e68bc58f6ac049930667","tid":36931,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">情憑誰來定錯對</span></span></blockquote><br />\n你呀媽總比我隊"},{"pid":"5239d43ed949f653da279d9a8d6fc852b3664644","tid":36931,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">情憑誰來定錯對</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條賓周